room_title: Escape room "The Light Room" by Nodus 805 Escape Rooms in Los Angeles
room_address: 80 Long Court Suite #2B Thousand Oaks, CA 91360
room_description: Years ago, Charles Batchelor became sick of listening to his close friend Thomas Edison comparing himself to his rival, Nikola Tesla. In order to finally put to rest who had the greatest mind between them, he devised the perfect way to test them. It was never known what test he conducted, until now.
